                          <q xml:lang="gez">
                            <seg part="I"><gap reason="ellipsis" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>ወከመ፡ ጢስ፡ ዘይወ<choice><sic>ጸ</sic><corr>ጽ</corr></choice>እ፡ እመሣ<choice><sic>ከ</sic><corr>ክ</corr></choice>ው፡ <choice><sic>ክ</sic><corr>ከ</corr></choice>ማሁ፡ ብዙህ፡ ህማማት፡ ወጽአ፡ እምላዕለ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ክርስቶስ፡ ተእህዘ፡ <sic>ተሰቀለ፡</sic> ሐመ፡ ተኰርዓ፡ ዘባኖ፡ ተዘብጠ፡ ወህየንተ፡ ማይ፡ ሀሞ<choice><sic>ት</sic><corr>ተ</corr></choice><supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ሰትየ፡<gap reason="ellipsis" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/></seg>
                          </q>
                        </item>

                        <item xml:id="a5">
